## Description ##
	This is Wordpress Plugin, Which is use for display responsive slideshow using shortcode [vaibhav_slider] on the post.
	
## Installation ##
1. Download Plugin. 
	[Download] (https://codeload.github.com/patelvaibhavr/vaibhav_slider) 

2. Install vaibhav_slider plugin from the 'Plugins' section in your dashboard (Plugins > Add New > Upload Plugin -> Select Plugin Zip File From your Downloaded Location).

3. Another Alternatively Way is that you can Unzip it and upload it to the plugins folder of your WordPress installation (wp-content/plugins/ directory of your WordPress installation).

4. Activate it through the 'Plugins' section.

5. Now Here we go. Installation is Complete.

## How To Use ##
1. As you Install & Activate plugin there is Vaibhav Slider Settings Page will be added in Settings Section (Settings > Vaibhav Slider Settings) OR  Last Option in List of Menu.

2. Here You can Add slide for your slider.

3. Select your slide image by Upload Image Button and click on Add Slide Button to Add Slide.

4. Here you can reorder your Images (by drag and drop) and save your slide order by click on save slider button.

5. You can delete the Image by click on 'X' button on your slide.

6. After you added your Images you can now use slideshow using [vaibhav_slider] shortcode.

7. Add New Post add shortcode [vaibhav_slider] in texteditor and publish the post. 

8. View your post, you can see your slideshow on your post.

Thank You...


